NG0737:426: rtsibs drug mu khyud ldan pa la //

NG0737:430: mu khyud rtsa ba'i srog sngags dang *//

NG0737:433: rdo rje lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bca' //

NG0737:435: bla rdo srog gi 'khor lo gsum //
